tton data-hasLike="0" data-imgId="<%=val._id%>" data-imgCreator="<%=data._id%>" class="like-btn" title="I like this"><i class="fa fa-thumbs-o-up"></i></button><span class="likes"><%=val.likes%></span> <button data-hasDislike="0" data-imgId="<%=val._id%>" data-imgCreator="<%=data._id%>" class="dislike-btn" title="I dislike this"><i class="fa fa-thumbs-o-down"></i></button><span class="dislikes"><%=val.dislikes%></span> <%}%> <p> <%=val.imgName%> </p><button class="delete-img-btn" data-imgId="<%=val._id%>">Delete Image</button> </div><%}) %> <div class="add-img-button"> <h3>Add Image</h3> <div class="hover-bg"></div></div></div><%}else{%> <h1 class="no-album-warning">It looks like you have not added any favorite image to your album page.<br>Here are some few tips to get you started</h1> <ol> <li>Visit the <a href="https://images.google.com/" target="_blank" class="google-image-link">Google Image Search Page</a> if you don't have any image links to use for creating your photo album </li><li>Search for your favorite thing</li><li>In the search results, click on the image thumbnail you like and want to use</li><li>A popup will show up with the larger version of the image, click on the view image button</li><li>Wait for the image to load, after loading copy the link in the address bar and come back to the website(Netbum)</li><li>Click on the add image button below, a popup will show up</li><li>Fill in the field that ask you of the image url by pasting in the link you copy from the google image search page</li><li>Fill the field that ask you of the image name</li><li>Click the Add button and you are done</li></ol> <div class="add-img-button" style="margin-left:50px;"> <h3>Add Image</h3> <div class="hover-bg"></div></div><%}%> </div><div class="img-add-dialog"> <span class="close-icon"><i class="fa fa-times-circle fa-2x"></i></span> <p class="img-add-general-error">Something went wrong, please try again</p><p class="img-name-error">Please enter a image name or caption</p><p